commit.message:
fix: avoid to call (file).readlines to reduce memory usage

(file).readlines() load all of the lines in input files to a lot of
memory space is required if input files are large. On the other hand,
file objects are iterators yields each lines until EOF and there is no
need to call readlines originally.
